F4\u63A5\u62A5\u9519\u3002</p><div class="language- line-numbers-mode"><button class="copy"></button><span class="lang"></span><pre><code><span class="line"><span style="color:#A6ACCD;">// var \u547D\u4EE4\u5B58\u5728\u53D8\u91CF\u63D0\u5347</span></span>
